name: Us Will Become I
description: We will commit suicide, become addicted to drugs, be hospitalized due to emotional eating disorder, be beaten-beaten, experience more trauma than his age, enter politics and cause thousands of deaths, starve, gamble, and be murdered by his/her/they girlfriend-wife, and every gift on tiktok live broadcasts will be taken away from him. We continue to bring individuals into the world who will disgrace themselves as a result of this, who believe that money is made up of pradas, who will give commands to others, who will work their entire lives to acquire a single house, and who will believe that they are living even when they are not.
